atley]] (born 1933)\n*[[Mark Helias]] (born 1950)\n*[[Jonas Hellborg]] (born 1958)\n*[[Michael Henderson]] (born 1951)\n*[[Shifty Henry]] (1921\u20131958) \n*[[Svante Henryson]] (born 1963)\n*[[Milt Hinton]] (1910\u20132000)\n*[[Derrick Hodge]] (born 1979)\n*[[Colin Hodgkinson]] (1945)\n*[[Sigurd Hole]] (born 1981)\n*[[Dave Holland]] (born 1946)\n*[[Major Holley]] (1924\u20131990)\n*[[Scotty Holt]]\n*[[Fred Hopkins]] (1947\u20131999))\n*[[Jim Hughart]] (born 1936)\n*[[Spike Hughes]] (1908\u20131987)\n*[[Stig Hvalryg]] (born 1960)\n\n==I==\n<!--Please don't add links to musicians for whom there is no article on Wikipedia; they will be removed.  There are a lot of gaps in Wikipedia's coverage of jazz, but either place a request for the article in question, or create one yourself. --><!--Please only add new entries for which there's an article; red-linked entries will be removed.  If a bassist really should be here, then start an article on him or her, and then add the link.-->\n*[[Dieter Ilg]] (born 1961)\n*[[Peter Ind]] (born 1928)\n*[[Dennis Irwin]] (1951\u20132008)\n*[[Itzam Cano]]\n*[[Jeff Irwin]] (born 1977)\n*[[Chuck Israels]] (born 1936)\n*[[Carl Morten Iversen]] (born 1948)\n*[[David Izenzon]] (1932\u20131979)\n\n==J==\n<!--Please don't add links to musicians for whom there is no article on Wikipedia; they will be removed.  There are a lot of gaps in Wikipedia's coverage of jazz, but either place a request for the article in question, or create one yourself. --><!--Please only add new entries for which there's an article; red-linked entries will be removed.  If a bassist really should be here, then start an article on him or her, and then add the link.-->\n[[File:Tord Gustavsen Trio.jpg|thumb|[[Harald Johnsen]] with [[Tord Gustavsen Trio]] in 2007, known for this collaboration and work with artists like <br/>[[Einar Iversen]], [[Ditlef Eckhoff]], [[Silje Nergaard]], [[Frode Barth]], [[Svein Olav Herstad]], and within [[Sigurd K\u00f8hn|K\u00f8hn]]/[[Nils-Olav 